An animated SVG brand icon component designed for headers, loading states, and brand identity. Customize colors and animations to match your application's theme.

## Sizes

Preset sizes from `xs` (16px) to `xl` (64px), or pass a custom pixel value.

```svelte preview title="Size Presets"
<BrandIcon size="xs" />
<BrandIcon size="sm" />
<BrandIcon size="md" />
<BrandIcon size="lg" />
<BrandIcon size="xl" />
