```

## Animations

Three animation styles for different use cases: `wave` draws strokes progressively, `pulse` creates a heartbeat effect, and `breathe` provides subtle opacity changes.

```svelte preview title="Animation Styles"
<BrandIcon size="lg" animation="wave" animationDuration={4} />
<BrandIcon size="lg" animation="pulse" animationDuration={3} />
<BrandIcon size="lg" animation="breathe" animationDuration={4} />
```

## Custom Colors

Use CSS variables or hex colors. The icon uses monochromatic strokes by default.

```svelte preview title="Brand Variants"
<BrandIcon size="lg" color="var(--accent-brand)" />
<BrandIcon size="lg" color="#22c55e" backgroundColor="#052e16" />
<BrandIcon size="lg" color="#3b82f6" backgroundColor="#1e3a5f" />
<BrandIcon size="lg" color="#a855f7" backgroundColor="#2e1065" />
```

